  "title": "Punchy! x Tiny Takeover",
  "description": "Hold your baby mobs in first person with animations, better experienced with Punchy.",
  "body": "<div>\n    <img\n    width=\"100%\"    \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cca5699bd7a66a33c1411fbdbae0ad410892b98a.png\"\n    alt=\"features\"\n  />\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <img\n    width=\"80%\"    \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FDqBVN2B/images/049bbd21fa6bffe1c747d1686aab04ee4086d8fd.gif\"\n    alt=\"features\"\n  />\n</div>\n\n<br>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<span>\nWe made this addon with lots of care for you, bringing a theme inspired by the new Minecraft update. <br> <strong>Fabric only for launch for now , we will consider porting this to other loaders and versions if we see demand!</strong><br>We plan to add more features in the future, join our Discord and share your ideas!\n<br>\n  <br>\n<strong>Warning! This is a server-side mod. Do not use it on servers with anti-cheat systems, as you may get banned.</strong>\n</span>\n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div align=\"center\">\n  \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/CXttaCyGCN\">\n  <img alt=\"discord\" width=\"60px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/25b3523cedf0cb3f3c12740f07400b5bc306954b.png\">\n</a><a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@mypunchymod\">\n  <img alt=\"tiktok\" width=\"60px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c455866e8b8d992e586e9d61e5cd905dcc6c84de.png\">\n</a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@punchyxp2\">\n  <img alt=\"youtube\" width=\"60px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c6ea4d87bf707d2f9f0bf59633d29ebede5c9fd7.png\">\n</a><a href=\"https://github.com/punchy-mod/punchy-wiki/wiki/\">\n  <img alt=\"github\" width=\"60px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0197a0dce279690de37a1f899b3d25edf9d3bac2.png\">\n</a><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/modinpunchy\">\n  <img alt=\"ko-fi\" width=\"60px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8a0c2971228a3266c56e4dcdeef1229af0974192.png\">\n</a>\n\n\n\n\n  \n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <div>\n    <iframe \n      width=\"560\" \n      height=\"315\" \n      src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MUWsQ1Riu6U?autoplay=1&mute=1\" \n      title=\"YouTube video player\" \n      frameborder=\"0\" \n      allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture\" \n      allowfullscreen>\n    </iframe>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<div>\n    <img\n    width=\"100%\"    \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cca5699bd7a66a33c1411fbdbae0ad410892b98a.png\"\n    alt=\"features\"\n  />\n</div>\n\n<br>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <img\n    width=\"220px\"    \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6b09dbb834c1380dbec2c950fb7091d806ba74d3.png\"\n    alt=\"features\"\n  />\n<br>\n<br>\n<img\nwidth=\"100%\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FDqBVN2B/images/3b1ad2ea8ee2437387ede0a61bda0b2adcc6939d.gif\"\nalt=\"features\"\n/>  \n<details>\n<summary>Play Stick</summary>\nWhen holding a stick and pressing a configurable keybind, the player throws the stick far away. The baby wolf runs after it, brings it back to the player, and then waits while looking at the player until the stick is taken from its mouth.\n</details>\n  <br>\n<img\nwidth=\"100%\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FDqBVN2B/images/2acaefde40b0a9d544fb86eb4668d172b8a52986.gif\"\nalt=\"features\"\n/>  \n<details>\n<summary>Play with Your Baby Wolf</summary>\nWhile holding the baby wolf, press the “I” keybind to trigger a playful animation with it..\n</details>\n<br>\n<img\nwidth=\"100%\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FDqBVN2B/images/9a0ea409bdb29da4b4c100d0885ee9d9328a4499.gif\"\nalt=\"features\"\n/>  \n<details>\n<summary>Carry Your Baby Mob</summary>\nCrouch and right-click to pick up your baby mob. The baby wolf has an exclusive animation. Press “I” while holding it in your arms.\n</details>\n<br>\n<img\nwidth=\"100%\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/FDqBVN2B/images/08b7dd7279fd6c0ea622029e6ae248ecc0120a8e.gif\"\nalt=\"features\"\n/>  \n<details>\n<summary>Whistle to Call Your Baby Wolf</summary>\nPress a configurable keybind to call the nearest baby wolf within a 1-chunk radius. If you have multiple baby wolves, press the alternate keybind to call all of them at once, regardless of distance.\n</details>\n\n\n</div>",
